\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211231 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5198017\charrsid10370956 Well, I'm eighty-two and I was born - if you can work it back - on the seventh of July. I never remember the year actually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16742072 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5198017\charrsid10370956 So that's in 1887.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211231 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5198017\charrsid10370956 Yes.
