{\*\xmlclose} - yes - yes - that's Middlesex isn't it. We lived in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Enfield{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, yes.
