\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16742072 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5198017\charrsid10370956 You married from home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211231 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5198017\charrsid10370956 Yes.
